onStart()

onResume()

5. ViewModels initialize
BaseMainActivityVm

MSDKInfoVm

MSDKManagerVM

6. DJI SDK background threads start
Registration

Product detection

USB monitoring

Link monitoring

7. USB broadcast receivers register
Your usbReceiver is here.

8. USB attach events fire
If a DJI controller is connected.